Ex Parte J. L. Bushiey. No. 16959. Delivered May 23, 1934.

The opinion states the case.

Scott & Hall, of Marshall, and Currie McCutcheon, of Dallas, for relator. Lloyd W. Davidson, State’s Attorney, of Austin, for the State. HAWKINS, Judge. —

The application herein is in all respects the same as that found in cause number *16,958, Ex parte Lee Burns. For the reason stated in the opinion in that case the writ herein requested is denied.

Writ denied.

(Reported on page 324 of this volume.)
